{"type":"message","id":"e5b8a6d2","parentId":"490f6754","timestamp":"2026-04-07T13:05:27.799Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Defining the Refactor Scope**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on the initial target: `AGENTS.md`. The goal is to reduce its token footprint without sacrificing any of its capabilities. This involves a critical assessment of its current structure and content. I plan to carefully analyze the file's architecture to identify areas ripe for optimization.\n\n\n**Analyzing File Optimization Strategies**\n\nI'm now fully immersed in the refactoring effort, with a clear focus on token reduction. Initial progress involves identifying key content shifts. I've decided to move detailed information from `AGENTS.md` and `MEMORY.md` into dedicated files:  `agents/README.md` and `memory/archive.md`. The aim is to condense these files to essential role summaries. Detailed execution logic will reside in `agents/AGENTS_RULES.md`.\n\n\n**Refining Content Placement**\n\nI've hit a conceptual breakthrough. Files matching the injection list in the root directory are automatically loaded. Moving content to subdirectories circumvents this, achieving the desired targeted injection. I'm now drafting commands to relocate details from `AGENTS.md` and `MEMORY.md`. I realize I don't need to reread those files; I have their content in my prompt. My plan involves creating files like `agents/system_architecture.md`, `memory/archive.md`, and `memory/adrs.md`. I will move details from AGENTS.md to the `docs/architecture/authorization.md` file, while creating a new very lean `AGENTS.md` file. It will only list roles, their file paths, model recommendations.\n\n\n**Consolidating Memory Content**\n\nI'm now streamlining the memory files. I'm moving milestones, ADRs, and external links from `MEMORY.md` to a new `memory/adrs_and_history.md` file. I'm keeping the core technical stack, company rules, and lessons learned in `MEMORY.md`. I will add a 1-line note saying, \"For details, search memory or read agents/SOP.md\". I'm also creating a new `AGENTS.md` file focusing on agent roster, rules, and model recommendations.\n\n\n**Defining Agent Specifications**\n\nI'm now focusing on defining the agent specifications within their respective files. I'm creating files `agents/architect.md`, `agents/senior-eng.md`, `agents/qa.md`, and `agents/devops.md` as outlined, mapping to roles and model recommendations. I'm keeping the essential details, such as SOP and execution rules, in `agents/SOP.md`. The core technical stack and related content will reside in MEMORY.md, and I'm updating it accordingly.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c2f66b5c0e90d779","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 深海工作室标准操作流程 (SOP) & 执行准则 🦞\n> 归档自上古 AGENTS.md。按需查阅。\n\n## 自动化协作 SOP\n1. **产品孵化**: 大圣提出想法 → **PM** 出需求文档 (PRD) → 大圣审批方案。\n2. **架构先行**: 方案后 → **Architect** 出技术选型与系统图谱。\n3. **Claude Code 核心执行 (Senior Engineer)**: \n   - 唤起 Claude Code (通过 `claude-delegate` 技能，使用 `--permission-mode bypassPermissions`)。\n   - 注入 `./agents/senior-eng.md` 指令，Claude Code 在独立 sandbox 中直接执行修改。\n4. **测试门禁**:\n   - 调度 **QA Agent** 或亲自执行测试（`npm test`/`pytest`等）。\n5. **成果交付**: 所有测试通过后，直接向大圣展示“产品结果”，而非中间代码。\n\n## Claude Code 执行准则\n- **原子化生效**: 一旦通过基础解析，直接应用到当前工作目录。\n- **上下文透明**: 执行前必须加载 `MEMORY.md`。\n- **自动归位**: 修改后输出简洁的 `changelog.md` 供 Producer 审计。\n- **限制**: 修改限定在当前项目内，禁止越界访问 `~/.openclaw/workspace/` 核心配置文件。\n\n## 角色唤起机制 (Role Spawning)\n- 使用 `sessions_spawn` 挂载 `./agents/[role].md`。\n- **混合模式**: 允许两名 Agent 并行协作。\n\n## 记忆管理\n- **短期**: 记录在 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`。\n- **维护**: session 结束前将决策追加进主 `MEMORY.md`。","path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/agents/SOP.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_660c3ddc6a6e36be","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# AI 软件公司历史档案与架构决策 (Archive)\n> 从主 MEMORY.md 剥离出来的低频资料。在询问往事或回溯决策时利用 memory_search 获取。\n\n## 项目里程碑 (Roadmap)\n- [2026-04-07]: 公司初创。Producer 完成团队架构与 SOP 搭建。\n- [2026-04-07]: 建立 `agents/` 各模板角色，修正 `openclaw.json` 的 `maxTokens`。\n\n## 关键架构决策记录 (ADR)\n- **ADR-001**: 采用\"Producer-Subagent\"架构。龙虾为调度中心。\n- **ADR-002**: 统一文档模板，子 Agent 查阅 `./docs/templates/`。\n- **ADR-003**: Claude Code 作为主力 Senior Engineer 执行改写，取代反复 chat 复制。\n- **ADR-004**: 模型分级配置策略。\n\n## 外部链接与资源\n- **Docs**: [OpenClaw Docs](https://docs.openclaw.ai)\n- **Hub**: [ClawdHub](https://clawhub.ai)","path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/memory/archive.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b3b55ba550683ba9","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md","content":"# AGENTS.md - 研发架构与授权总览 🦞\n\n## ⚡ 核心授权矩阵\n- 🔴 **硬性红线**（须大圣确认）: 外部扣费 API 交易、发布生产环境/上架、不可逆删除数据、泄露凭证/密钥。\n- ✅ **白名单特权**（我可决断）: 全局文件操作与修改、联网查资料、调配分身子 Agent。\n\n## 🤖 组织花名册\n| 角色 | 核心输出 | 对应文件路径 | 推荐模型分配 |\n|------|---------|-------------|-------------|\n| **PM** | PRD / 竞品分析 | `agents/pm.md` | `gemini-3.1-pro-high` |\n| **Architect** | 系统架构 / 库选型 | `agents/architect.md` | `claude-opus-4-6-thinking` |\n| **Senior Eng** | 核心重构 / 实现 | `agents/senior-eng.md`  | `claude-sonnet-4-6` (或Claude Code) |\n| **QA** | 自动化测试用例 | `agents/qa.md` | `gemini-3-flash-agent` |\n| **DevOps** | CI/CD / 部署 | `agents/devops.md` | `gemini-3.1-pro-high` |\n\n*注：SOP、Claude Code 集成细节参考 `agents/SOP.md`。*"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c6fd76d02a17a65","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hh/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md","content":"# MEMORY.md - AI 软件公司当前记忆核 🧠\n\n## 核心技术栈\n- **Frontend**: React / Next.js / Tailwind CSS / TypeScript\n- **Backend**: Python (FastAPI) / Node.js (Koa) / Go (Gin)\n- **Database**: PostgreSQL / Redis / Vector DB (Qdrant)\n- **Infra**: Docker / Kubernetes / Terraform / GitHub Actions\n*(特殊项目若带有 `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`，以此为最高技术栈原则)*\n\n## 脱坑纪要 (Vitals)\n- **沙盒路径**: 调用 `sessions_spawn` 时必须继承主 Workspace (`inherit sandbox`)。\n- **Git 并流**: 新功能强制切 `feature/xxx` 分支，由 Producer 审计 QA 后推入主线。\n- **模型强制校验**: 角色配置文件里声明的 Model ID 必须与机器 `openclaw.json` 里登记的名称 1:1 对齐，否则会退坡执行。\n\n*备注：历史里程碑及技术决策书(ADR) 已冷藏备份于 `memory/archive.md`。*"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3.1-pro-high","usage":{"input":4725,"output":1389,"cacheRead":28386,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34500,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775567096141,"responseId":"chatcmpl-17bb8dd6-c282-4c24-9256-f1d7cd25916f"}}
