{"type":"message","id":"2c571084","parentId":"10cc657e","timestamp":"2026-04-07T13:15:43.222Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Assessing User's Actions**\n\nI've noted the user uninstalled the extension and plans further testing with token sending. This suggests an active troubleshooting approach. My focus is now on the implications of their actions and understanding the exact nature of the observed issues after the uninstall process.\n\n\n**Confirming Reduced Payload**\n\nI see the user has uninstalled `openclaw-lark`, which I predicted would yield a significant reduction in payload size. Removing those Feishu JSON schemas is the key. Coupled with the markdown cleanup, the token count should be incredibly low now. My response will be enthusiastic and validating, speaking directly to their actions.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大圣，手起刀落，非常果断。\n\n飞书插件卸载后，这套系统里最吃上下文的“重灾区”（几十个极其复杂的工具 JSON Schema 结构定义）就彻底从每次的静默发送里剔除了。\n\n加上我们刚才砍掉的 90% 本地文档体积（去除了 `IDENTITY` 和 `TOOLS` 的全量注入，极致压缩了其他五个核心文档），现在的底座绝对是“轻如燕”的状态。\n\n你现在看新的请求日志，基础消耗（底噪）不出意外应该会**断崖式骤降到 2000 ~ 3000 Token 级别**（只剩下系统最基础的读写执行工具和那几百字的设定）。\n\n测完确认没问题的话，随时叫我，我们轻装上阵开搞新项目 🦞！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3.1-pro-high","usage":{"input":1506,"output":188,"cacheRead":73293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74987,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775567728980,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2ab25aea-9dfe-46d0-831e-41cabfc4d71f"}}
